93
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:48,870
Rancangan sukar berjalan lancar.

94
00:05:48,870 --> 00:05:50,120
Bagus.

95
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,870
Bagaimana jika saya gagal?

96
00:05:51,870 --> 00:05:53,450
Kita juga ada risiko.

97
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:59,040
Jika nak lawan awak,
pihak lawan pasti akan guna cahaya.

98
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:02,330
Dengan ini, kita boleh tahu
lokasi mereka berpandukan cahaya itu.

99
00:06:02,330 --> 00:06:06,290
Bayang Kegelapan tak dapat bergerak
jika mereka lancarkan cahaya.

100
00:06:06,290 --> 00:06:07,790
Biarpun Kuroiro buat kesilapan,

101
00:06:07,790 --> 00:06:10,330
