dan serang mereka.

102
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:14,290
Pelan A dah gagal.

103
00:06:14,290 --> 00:06:16,790
Kita berundur dulu.

104
00:06:17,910 --> 00:06:19,750
Tukar kepada pelan B.

105
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:22,830
Giliran awak pula, Komori.

106
00:06:24,950 --> 00:06:27,830
Cendawan tumbuh tak henti-henti.

107
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:29,620
Bencinya!

108
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:32,450
Berdasarkan dua tahap serangan lawan,

109
00:06:32,450 --> 00:06:34,950
