ramalkan cara kita lawan Kuroiro.

110
00:06:34,950 --> 00:06:37,290
Kendo memang hebat.

111
00:06:37,290 --> 00:06:39,040
Semua, tolong bertenang.

112
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,950
